and he wondered if any of the poor stout black men of parg were left to be unloaded and crated and shipped inland in those obnoxious drays .
when the galley landed at a quay of spongy rock a nightmare horde of wiggled out of the hatches , and two of them seized carter and dragged him ashore .
the smell and aspect of that city are beyond telling , and carter held only scattered images of the tiled streets and black doorways and endless precipices of grey vertical walls without windows .
